<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="514" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,432,534]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,359,432,458]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Distribution.</emphasis>
First record for Europe. This species was known from 
<collectingCountry box="[1004,1092,433,459]" name="Algeria" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Algeria</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1148,1218,433,459]" name="Egypt" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Egypt</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Rozkosny, R." box="[1233,1422,433,459]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514" pagination="1 - 105" refId="ref12466" refString="Rozkosny, R. (1977) The West Palaearctic species of Nemotelus Geoffroy (Diptera, Stratiomyidae). Folia Facultatis Scientiarum Naturalium Universitatis Purkynianae Brunensis, 17, Biologia, 51 (3), 1 - 105." type="journal article" year="1977">Rozkošný 1977</bibRefCitation>
), and was recently recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[549,620,471,497]" name="Libya" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Libya</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Troiano, G. &amp; Toscano, E." box="[637,949,471,497]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514" pagination="499 - 510" refId="ref12872" refString="Troiano, G. &amp; Toscano, E. (1997) Elenco degli Stratiomyidae paleartici del Museo Civico di Storia naturale &quot; G. Doria &quot; di Genova (Diptera). Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale &quot; G. Doria &quot;, 91, 499 - 510." type="journal article" year="1997">Troiano &amp; Toscano 1997</bibRefCitation>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[972,1062,471,497]" name="Tunisia" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Tunisia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hauser, M." box="[1079,1241,471,497]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514" pagination="591 - 601" refId="ref10817" refString="Hauser, M. (2008) Order Diptera, family Stratiomyidae. In: Harten, A. van (Ed.), Arthropod Fauna of the UAE, 1. Dar Al Ummah Printing, Publishing, Distribution &amp; Advertising, Abu Dhabi, pp. 591 - 601." type="book chapter" year="2008">Hauser 2008</bibRefCitation>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[1263,1331,471,497]" name="Israel" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Israel</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hauser, M." pageId="7" pageNumber="514" pagination="591 - 601" refId="ref10817" refString="Hauser, M. (2008) Order Diptera, family Stratiomyidae. In: Harten, A. van (Ed.), Arthropod Fauna of the UAE, 1. Dar Al Ummah Printing, Publishing, Distribution &amp; Advertising, Abu Dhabi, pp. 591 - 601." type="book chapter" year="2008">Hauser 2008</bibRefCitation>
) and the 
<collectingCountry box="[319,576,508,534]" name="United Arab Emirates" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">United Arab Emirates</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hauser, M." box="[591,747,508,534]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514" pagination="591 - 601" refId="ref10817" refString="Hauser, M. (2008) Order Diptera, family Stratiomyidae. In: Harten, A. van (Ed.), Arthropod Fauna of the UAE, 1. Dar Al Ummah Printing, Publishing, Distribution &amp; Advertising, Abu Dhabi, pp. 591 - 601." type="book chapter" year="2008">Hauser 2008</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
